----------------
 0 | 0 | 1 | 2 |
----------------
 1 | 1 | 0 | 1 |
----------------
 2 | 2 | 1 | 0 |
----------------}

Now going from state 0 (first row) to state 2 (third column) costs 2 steps as by implication this transition must pass through the intermediate state 1.

